value.title: ‘Birtherism’ Lies About Kamala Harris Exceed Those About Obama

value.title: Biden's once maligned digital operation raises big money by embodying candidate
value.excerpt: When Rob Flaherty began describing Joe Biden's digital strategy as a "battle for the soul of the Internet" earlier this year, the Democratic primary had barely ended, the former vice president's campaign was alarmingly low on money and President Donald Trump's digital-centric campaign looked like a juggernaut.
